ext_descriptions.ext_description:
the numerical measure of the selected angle at the point of intersection between two 
Shape_elements 
is the larger absolute value;

ul.li:
an annotation of "-0,3" is represented with a 

			value of -0.3 and an 

			value of 0;

an annotation of "+0,02" is represented with a 

			value of 0 and an 

			value of +0,02;

an annotation of "+1/+0,5" is represented with a 

			value of +0,5 and an 

			value of +1;

an annotation of "+1/-0,5" is represented with a 

			value of -0.5 and an 

			value of +1;

an annotation of "-1/-2,5" is represented with a 

			value of -2,5 and an 

			value of -1;
